Package nusri.fyp.demo.entity

Class PresetNode

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.entity.PresetNode
@Entity public class PresetNode extends Object
PresetNode entity representing a single step in a preset workflow.
It uses PresetNodeId as a composite key and links to the specific Preset. It also contains node information such as name, quota, parent nodes, and triggerable actions.
